<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="background-color: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></span></font><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Your business insurance is now up for renewal with Kingsbridge.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Have you considered adding&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">IR35 Protect</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;to your cover?</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Our IR35 Protect cover&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">protects your business from the potentially crippling costs that can follow an IR35 enquiry</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. They can include defence costs, taxes and interest — on top of any penalties payable to HMRC.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">I’ve attached some information about our IR35 Protect cover in case you’d like to know more.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Or if you'd prefer to talk through it in more detail, or would like to get it added to your renewal quote, please give me a call on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
